OL,5,G2200 999: Critical Condition
OL,6,     FHaving plummeted 15 feet onto
OL,7,     Fconcrete, Michael is rushed into
OL,8,     Fresus with a significant
OL,9,     Flaceration to his head. And a
OL,10,     Fdriver has a crushed leg after
OL,11,     Fbeing run over by his own van.
OL,12,G2300 He Kills Coppers
OL,13,     FThree policemen are murdered
OL,14,     Fduring the 1966 World Cup
OL,15,     Fcelebrations, and three men are
OL,16,     Fconnected to the deaths: policeman
OL,17,     FFrank; journalist and witness
OL,18,     FTony; and Billy - the murderer.
OL,19,     F(Ep1/3)
