OL,5,G0005 He Kills Coppers
OL,6,     FBilly goes on the run, while
OL,7,     Freporter Tony is in demand as the
OL,8,     Facknowledged expert on the cop
OL,9,     Fkiller. But five years on, Frank's
OL,10,     Flife is blighted by his failure to
OL,11,     Fcapture the villain. (Ep2/3)
OL,12,G0105 He Kills Coppers
OL,13,     FNearly 20 years after the
OL,14,     Fkillings, Frank is prompted into
OL,15,     Frenewed action by the
OL,16,     Fdisappearance of journalist Tony,
OL,17,     Fand finally manages to locate
OL,18,     FBilly. (Ep3/3)
