OL,5,G0210 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FThe pursuit of a white van tearing
OL,7,     Fup the turf proves to be a family
OL,8,     Faffair, and a two-year-old German
OL,9,     Fshepherd cross named Titan earns
OL,10,     Fhis spurs.
OL,11,G0300 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FDog handler Darren calls on all
OL,13,     Fhis powers of persuasion to try
OL,14,     Fand end a rooftop stand-off, and
OL,15,     FSteve is forced to use his pepper
OL,16,     Fspray on a suspect.
